Path Recruitment Message 14

Date: 02/15/2023

Happy Hump Day, everyone! As we reach the halfway point of this recruitment drive, I want to take a moment to thank everyone who has joined us so far. Your dedication and enthusiasm are truly inspiring. For those who haven't joined yet, don't worry - there's still plenty of time to hop on board.

Remember, being a part of The Simian Path means more than just a membership - it means joining a community of like-minded individuals who share a passion for exploration and discovery. Whether you're a seasoned researcher or just starting out, there's a place for you here. So why not take the leap and see where it takes you?

And for those of you who might be feeling hesitant, just remember: every journey begins with a single step. We may be on Day 14, but that's just the start of our journey together. Let's make the most of it, and see where the Path takes us next.

Together, we are unstoppable.

Join us and be a part of The Path.
